data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. **ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN AT 3.125%** available for qualifying buyers.  PRICE DROP! Motivated seller!  Bring ALL Offers!  Don't miss this opportunity to own a LAKE FRONT Home with community BOAT RAMP at Calabay Parc at Tower Lake.  Conveniently located with easy access to shopping, dining, golfing, and all the attractions of Central Florida.  Airbnb and Short Term Rentals allowed.  LIKE NEW Custom exquisite 4-bedroom, 2 and a half bathrooms lakefront.  Step inside to discover an open-concept living area bathed in natural light, with gleaming engineered hardwood floors and high ceilings. The well-appointed kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a large island, making it perfect for hosting gatherings.  The four spacious bedrooms include a luxurious master suite on the main floor and three additional bedrooms on the lower floor that provide plenty of space for family and guests.  Enjoy stunning sunsets from the balcony.  Launch your boat from the community boat ramp, go fishing, or simply take in the beauty of the lake.  This lakefront gem is a rare find, offering the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and natural beauty.  HOA includes Lawn and Sprinkler Maintenance, Lake Upkeep, Manned Gard Gate and Common Area Maintenance.
